text: Emphytoecia sutura-alba is a species of beetle in the family Cerambycidae. It was described by Fairmaie and Germain in 1859. It is known from Chile.BioLib.cz - Emphytoecia sutura-alba. Retrieved on 8 September 2014. ==References== Category:Lamiinae Category:Beetles described in 1859
